    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Huuarnari">Vuarneri</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>bone memorie <name ref="Warnefredus"
                            >Vuarnifridi</name></persName> riceve da <persName ref="#people/214"
                            key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane
                        ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario
                        nomine (…), <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> illa cuius vocabulum est
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/304" key="#Churches">beati Sancti
                            Angeli</orgName>, sitas loco ubi vocitatur ad <placeName
                            ref="#places/2100">Monte</placeName>, pertenens <orgName
                            key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/269">ecclesie Sancte
                            Marie</orgName>, quod est <rs key="#Baptismal_churches">plebe
                            batismales</rs> sitas loco <placeName ref="#places/165"
                            key="#Baptismal_churches">Sexto</placeName>, quod est de suppotestatem
                        ipsius <rs key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Baptismal_churches #Mother_churches"
                            >Sancti Martini</orgName>; ecclesia vero ipsa Sancti Angeli cum casis
                        domnicatis quam et massariciis, cum fundamentis et universis fabricis suis,
                        seu curtis, ortis, terris, vineis, olivis, silvis, virgareis, pratis,
                        pascuis, cultis rebus vel incultis, omnia quantum ad suprascripta ecclesia
                        Sancti Angeli est pertenentes in integrum mihi eas dedisti, tali ordinem ut
                        da admodum in mea (…) qui de meis heredes sit potestatem (…) abendi,
                        inperandi, gubernandi, laborare faciendi et nobis eas privatum nomine
                        usufructuandi, ita ut melioretur nam non pegioretur; et in ipsa ecclesia
                        Sancti Angeli per nostra dispositionem officium Dei et luminaria seu
                        missarum solemnia fieri debeas (…). Censo: pro omni censum et iustitia
                        exinde tibi vel ad subcessoribus tuis ad parte ipsius ecclesie Sancte Marie,
                        per singulos annos, in omne mense ianuario, per nos aut per misso nostro
                        vobis vel ad ministeriales vestro, quas in ipsa ecclesia Sancte Marie pre
                        tempore fuerit censum vobis reddere debeamus argentum soledos tres de bonos
                        denarios expendiviles, per singulos soledos duodecim denarios rationatos; et
                        hominibus illis qui in suprascriptis casis abitantes fuerint, nos eos a
                        mandato vestro hic Luca venire faciamus legem rt iustitiam faciendum tantum.
                        Pena: (…) spondeo ego qui supra Vuarneri una cum meis heredes conponere tibi
                        (…) penam argentum soledos triginta (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Witness #Notary"><name ref="Lopo">Lopo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ildebaldus">Ildipaldo</name></persName>,
                            <persName ref="#people/147" key="#Witness">Lamberto</persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudebertus"
                            >Teupertus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> filio <persName> quondam <name
                                ref="Deusdedit">Deusdedit</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rotardus">Rottardo</name></persName> filio
                            <persName> quondam <name ref="Domnibertus">Domniperti</name></persName>,
                            <persName ref="#people/149" key="#Witness">Cunimundo</persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
